{"tid":6831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"寄聖誕卡比各位巴絲","createTime":"2016-11-27T14:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T13:28:53.000Z","uid":18900,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59dc4f3decd41e4a8d62787910099f259ea8910e","tid":6831,"uid":18900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"先自介少少<br />\n我係一個中佬差唔多四十，而家係一個無車無樓既IT從業員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 經歷過每年寄好多聖誕卡比朋友親戚又收到好多聖誕卡。<br />\n<br />\n到後來既e card再到近年whatsapp算<br />\n但始終我係一個唔潮又老土既人，懷念以前個世界。<br />\n<br />\n所以想攪個少活動，如果有巴絲想收聖誕卡，請email比我，講低地址同名仲有巴定絲，幾歲同埋讀書定做野，最好話我知讀咩科同做咩工作<br />\n<br />\n如果你有野問或者有野想我回應可以寫低，如果冇我就隨心而寫<br />\n<br />\n大約十二月十號寄唔會太遲<br />\n一切只在一份單純的信任<br />\n<br />\n呢度好似冇pm<br />\n所以請email去it.manager.kwok@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n唔知會唔會結果都係單機mode呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647d3f24a34aba9f2e9246f0c60c4e83db99e790","tid":6831,"uid":18900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"始終要返工唔可以成玩咩十年<br />\n<br />\n我會每日推一推貼"},{"pid":"5dcc3a18a6f7b28ce9b0d7419ab4d7448e262953","tid":6831,"uid":8942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d150d71ca8f102714e1f8f9511578be8158a3cc5","tid":6831,"uid":8828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"名已留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e947e99160d1928ac268be33db8d1791b66cc0","tid":6831,"uid":18900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ada05d153c16f153ed28d42eea1b4f1b351d38","tid":6831,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:15:03